    "description": "<strong> ~ ~ ~ ~ Welcome To Chicken Fight ~ ~ ~ ~</strong><br>Chicken Fight is a platformer beat 'em up where you utilize your environment to defeat your enemies who consist of mutant frogs, werewolves, and even other chickens. There is a variety of modes, maps and gamemodes to play for everyone to enjoy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/90edaeb5f4be945eee28823d7eff527b.poster.avif?t=1684181363\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/90edaeb5f4be945eee28823d7eff527b.webm?t=1684181363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/90edaeb5f4be945eee28823d7eff527b.mp4?t=1684181363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> ~ ~ ~ ~ PVP ~ ~ ~ ~</strong><br>Fight in unique maps and gamemodes, local and online combined.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/286209fc8f9311d5b530d0f91b3594fd.poster.avif?t=1684181363\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/286209fc8f9311d5b530d0f91b3594fd.webm?t=1684181363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/286209fc8f9311d5b530d0f91b3594fd.mp4?t=1684181363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>(Controller required for local multiplayer, only one keyboard input device allowed)<br><br><strong> ~ ~ ~ ~ Story Mode ~ ~ ~ ~</strong><br>Explore a series of levels, all very unique from each other and filled with fun platforming and cool secrets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/6d83a9462daf3c7396e967cc10da0bfd.poster.avif?t=1684181363\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/6d83a9462daf3c7396e967cc10da0bfd.webm?t=1684181363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/6d83a9462daf3c7396e967cc10da0bfd.mp4?t=1684181363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>(Controller required for local multiplayer, only one keyboard input device allowed)<br><br><strong> ~ ~ ~ ~ Map Editor ~ ~ ~ ~</strong><br>Think of creative new ways to play the game and create fun levels for people to fight in.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/bb271da4137af61eb715f10456fd53e6.poster.avif?t=1684181363\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/bb271da4137af61eb715f10456fd53e6.webm?t=1684181363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159470/extras/bb271da4137af61eb715f10456fd53e6.mp4?t=1684181363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
